Package: ubumirror
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, cron, rsync
Recommends: postfix | mail-transport-agent, apache2 | httpd
Suggests: vsftpd | proftpd
Description: Ubuntu mirror scripts
 This package contains scripts for mirroring various parts of the Ubuntu
 infrastructure.
 .
 This includes archives packages, ISO files for releases, daily builds for ISO
 files from cdimage and DVD images.
